Preconditions:
- The input array `nums` must not be null.
- The length of the input array `nums` must be at least 2.
- The elements in the input array `nums` must be non-negative integers.

Postconditions:
- The return value must be an integer.
- The return value must be the maximum width of a ramp in the input array `nums`.
- If there is no ramp in the input array `nums`, the return value must be 0.